1. *Pardon* što kasnim na sastanak. (Excuse me for being late to the meeting.)
2. Izvinite, nisam dobro čuo, *pardon*. (Sorry, I didn't hear well, pardon.)
3. *Pardonom* što vas prekidam, ali mislim da to nije tačno. (With all due respect, I believe that is not correct.)
4. *Pardonirajte* me na nespretnosti, nisam to namjerno uradio. (Please forgive me for being clumsy, I didn't do it on purpose.)
5. Molim vas, *pardon*, da li ste vidjeli moj telefon? (Excuse me, have you seen my phone, pardon?)
6. *Pardoniram* vašu grešku, ali to nije ono što sam tražio. (I pardon your mistake, but that is not what I asked for.)
7. *Pardon* što sam uzeo vašu olovku, nisam znao da je vaša. (Sorry for taking your pen, I didn't know it was yours.)
8. Ne mogu doći na sastanak, *pardon* zbog porodičnih obaveza. (I cannot come to the meeting, pardon me due to family obligations.)
9. *Pardonirajte* moj loš srpski, još učim jezik. (Please excuse my poor Serbian, I'm still learning the language.)
10. Izvinite što smetam, *pardon*, ali trebam vašu pomoć. (Sorry to bother you, pardon, but I need your help.)